Description:
The zip file contains all codes of Assignment 1 for image segmentation and evaluation.

Operating Environment:
1. System environment: Mac OS X 10.11 EI Captian
2. IDE: MATLAB R2015b and Xcode 8.2.1

Installation Notes:
1) Unzip the files.
2) You need to follow the README files on Normalized cut and gPb-owt-ucm for compilation instructions. (The code is based Mixed-Language Programming Language)
3) After you got all segmentation results, change the input file path of evaluation code according to different segmentation results paths.